msgstr "`/home/jboss` 是基础镜像 和 中所有 quarkus 二进制 `ubi8/openjdk-11-runtime` `ubi8/openjdk-17-runtime` link:https://catalog.redhat.com/software/containers/ubi8/openjdk-17/618bdbf34ae3739687568813?container-tabs=dockerfile[文件] 的工作目录（ link:https://catalog.redhat.com/software/containers/ubi8/openjdk-17/618bdbf34ae3739687568813?container-tabs=dockerfile[ubi8/openjdk-17-runtime 的 Dockerfile] ）。"

#. type: Title ===
#: _versions/2.13/guides/container-image.adoc
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid "Multi-module projects and layering"
msgstr "多模块项目与分层"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/2.13/guides/container-image.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"When building a multi-module project containing a Quarkus application as one module and various supporting project dependencies as other modules,\n"
"Quarkus supports placing these supporting modules in a separate container image layer from the rest of the application dependencies, with the expectation\n"
"that these supporting modules will change more frequently than the regular application dependencies - thus making a rebuild faster if the\n"
"application dependencies have not changed."
msgstr "在构建一个多模块项目时，该项目包含一个作为模块的 Quarkus 应用程序以及作为其他模块的各种支持性项目依赖项， Quarkus 支持将这些辅助模块放置在与其余应用程序依赖项不同的容器镜像层中，因为预计这些辅助模块的变更频率会高于常规的应用程序依赖项——这样，如果应用程序依赖项未发生变更，重建速度就会更快。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/2.13/guides/container-image.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"To enable this feature, the property `quarkus.bootstrap.workspace-discovery` needs to be set to `true` either as a system property\n"
"when invoking the build tool, either as a build tool property. Setting this property in `application.properties` will **not** work because\n"
"this property needs to be known very early on in the build process."
msgstr "要启用此功能，需要将属性 `quarkus.bootstrap.workspace-discovery` 设置为 `true，` 该设置既可以作为调用构建工具时的系统属性，也可以作为构建工具属性。在 `application.properties` 中设置此属性将 *无法* 生效，因为该属性需要在构建过程的非常早期阶段就被识别。"

#. type: Title ==
#: _versions/2.13/guides/container-image.adoc
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid "Docker"
msgstr "Docker"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/2.13/guides/container-image.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The extension `quarkus-container-image-docker` is using the Docker binary and the generated Dockerfiles under `src/main/docker` in order to perform Docker builds."
msgstr "`quarkus-container-image-docker` 扩展通过使用 Docker 二进制文件以及 `src/main/docker` 目录下生成的 Dockerfile 文件来执行 Docker 构建。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/2.13/guides/container-image.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "To use this feature, add the following extension to your project."
msgstr "要使用此功能，请将以下扩展程序添加到您的项目中。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/2.13/guides/container-image.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The `quarkus-container-image-docker` extension is capable of https://docs.docker.com/buildx/working-with-buildx/#build-multi-platform-images/[creating multi-platform (or multi-arch)] images using https://docs.docker.com/engine/reference/commandline/buildx_build/[`docker buildx build`]. See the `quarkus.docker.buildx.*` configuration items in the <<#DockerOptions,Docker Options>> section below."
msgstr "`quarkus-container-image-docker` 扩展能够使用 link:https://docs.docker.com/engine/reference/commandline/buildx_build/[docker buildx build] link:https://docs.docker.com/buildx/working-with-buildx/#build-multi-platform-images/[命令创建多平台（或多架构）] 镜像。请参阅下 xref:DockerOptions[文“Docker 选项] ”部分中的 `quarkus.docker.buildx.*` 配置项。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/2.13/guides/container-image.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "`docker buildx build` ONLY supports https://docs.docker.com/engine/reference/commandline/buildx_build/#load[loading the result of a build] to `docker images` when building for a single platform. Therefore, if you specify more than one argument in the `quarkus.docker.buildx.platform` property, the resulting images will not be loaded into `docker images`. If `quarkus.docker.buildx.platform` is omitted or if only a single platform is specified, it will then be loaded into `docker images`."
msgstr "`docker buildx build` 仅在针对单一平台进行构建时，才支持 link:https://docs.docker.com/engine/reference/commandline/buildx_build/#load[将构建结果加载] 到 `Docker 镜像中` 。 因此，如果在 `quarkus.docker.buildx.platform` 属性中指定了多个参数，生成的镜像将不会被加载到 `Docker 镜像中` 。如果省略 `quarkus.docker.buildx.platform` 属性，或者仅指定了一个平台，则生成的镜像将被加载到 `Docker 镜像中` 。"

#. type: Title ==
#: _versions/2.13/guides/container-image.adoc
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid "S2I"
msgstr "S2I"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/2.13/guides/container-image.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The extension `quarkus-container-image-s2i` is using S2I binary builds in order to perform container builds inside the OpenShift cluster.\n"
"The idea behind the binary build is that you just upload the artifact and its dependencies to the cluster and during the build they will be merged to a builder image (defaults to `fabric8/s2i-java`)."
msgstr "`quarkus-container-image-s2i` 扩展使用 S2I 二进制构建，以便在 OpenShift 集群内执行容器构建。二进制构建背后的理念是，你只需将工件及其依赖关系上传到集群，然后在构建过程中将它们合并到构建器镜像中（默认为 `fabric8/s2i-java` ）。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/2.13/guides/container-image.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The benefit of this approach, is that it can be combined with OpenShift's `DeploymentConfig` that makes it easy to roll out changes to the cluster."
msgstr "这种方法的优势在于，它可以与 OpenShift 的 `DeploymentConfig` 结合使用，从而能够轻松地将变更部署到集群中。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/2.13/guides/container-image.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"S2I builds require creating a `BuildConfig` and two `ImageStream` resources, one for the builder image and one for the output image.\n"
"The creation of such objects is being taken care of by the Quarkus Kubernetes extension."
msgstr "S2I 构建需要创建一个 `BuildConfig` 和两个 `ImageStream` 资源，一个用于构建镜像，一个用于输出镜像。Quarkus Kubernetes 扩展负责创建此类对象。"

